WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.600
Tomorrow, I’ll buy Kyoko-chan a slice of cake to thank her for taking notes for me while I was away from school.

00:06.000 --> 00:08.520
It’s been a long time since we’ve gone to fool around in the city together.

00:08.520 --> 00:14.120
Going out right after school is a no-no, but everybody else does it.

00:14.120 --> 00:15.920
Why can’t I, every great now-and-then?

00:16.560 --> 00:19.880
Oh, I’ll have to ask Mom for some money.

00:20.380 --> 00:24.260
I’d better buy Mom and Dad something while I’m out.
